text: Vladimír Kudrna (22 December 1923 - 2 November 1991) was a Czech sports shooter. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1923 births Category:1991 deaths Category:Czech male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Czechoslovakia Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Prague
